		<pubDate>Fri, 26 Feb 2021 00:00:00 -0300</pubDate>
		<link>https://mountaineerbr.github.io/blog/25/</link>
		<dc:language>en</dc:language>
		<category>topics/scripts/t√≥picos/bitcoin/volunteer work/trabalho volunt√°rio/work/trabalho/confiss√µes de bi√≥logo/confessions of a biologist/nasa perseverance rover/commentaries/coment√°rios/astronomy/astronomia/personal update</category>
